General.Name: Hamashbir 365 Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Hamashbir 365 Holdings Ltd. operates departmental stores in Israel. The company provides men's, women's, and children's fashion products; home styling products; and holiday shopping, garden, computer and electricity, tourism and leisure, pharma, sport, and other products. It also offers gift cards. The company was formerly known as Hamashbir Lazarchan Ltd. and changed its name to Hamashbir 365 Holdings Ltd. in March 2012. Hamashbir 365 Holdings Ltd. was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Netanya, Israel. Hamashbir 365 Holdings Ltd. is a subsidiary of Shavit-Gitarts Group Ltd.
